  "bobBuildPrompt": "# IBM Bob Build Prompt: Smart Attendance Management System\n\nBuild a complete smart attendance management system for colleges with role-based dashboards (Admin, Teacher, Student), attendance marking, reporting, and CSV export capabilities.\n\n## Tech Stack\n- Frontend: React + Vite + Tailwind CSS\n- Backend: Node.js + Express\n- Database: SQLite\n- Authentication: JWT\n\n## Key Features\n1. User authentication with role-based access (Admin, Teacher, Student)\n2. Class management (CRUD operations)\n3. Student enrollment management\n4. Attendance marking by teachers\n5. Attendance reports with date range filtering\n6. CSV export functionality\n7. Dashboard for each user role\n8. Responsive design\n\n## Database Schema (6 tables)\n1. users - User accounts with roles\n2. classes - Course/class information\n3. students - Student details\n4. class_enrollments - Student-class relationships\n5. attendance_records - Daily attendance data\n6. attendance_reports - Generated reports\n\n## Implementation Priority\n1. Set up project structure\n2. Implement authentication system\n3. Build database schema\n4. Create API endpoints\n5. Build frontend dashboards\n6. Implement attendance marking\n7. Add reporting and CSV export\n8. Testing and deployment\n\nPlease build this application following best practices for security, performance, and code quality.",
